OL,3,CMassachusetts governor 'legalises'
OL,4,Chaggis in symbolic nod to Scotland fans
OL,6,FThe governor of Massachusetts declared
OL,7,Fthat she has "legalised" haggis, in a
OL,8,Fsymbolic nod to Scottish fans as they
OL,9,Fcontinue their World Cup takeover of
OL,10,FBoston.
OL,12,FDuring media interviews on Thursday,
OL,13,FMaura Healey signed an executive order
OL,14,Fbrought to her in jest by Scottish
OL,15,Fpodcaster David McIntosh Jr.
OL,17,F"We've made haggis legal in
OL,18,FMassachusetts," Healey said in a video
OL,19,Fposted online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
