OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781853482
OL,3,CMassachusetts governor 'legalises'
OL,4,Chaggis in symbolic nod to Scotland fans
OL,6,FIndividual states cannot override
OL,7,Ffederal food safety and import rules,
OL,8,Fso there is still a long way to go
OL,9,Fbefore the traditional Scottish
OL,10,Fdelicacy is on supermarket shelves.
OL,12,FHaggis is made from sheep's innards -
OL,13,Fthe heart, liver and lungs - the
OL,14,Flatter of which has been illegal to
OL,15,Fserve in the US since the early 1970s,
OL,16,Fleaving Scottish producers with no way
OL,17,Fof exporting it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
