OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781853482
OL,3,CMassachusetts governor 'legalises'
OL,4,Chaggis in symbolic nod to Scotland fans
OL,6,FEating livestock lungs was banned in
OL,7,Fthe US over safety concerns, and
OL,8,Finstead, simplified versions of haggis
OL,9,Fare sold, often with chicken liver and
OL,10,Fground lamb.
OL,12,FThe seemingly symbolic gesture by
OL,13,FGovernor Healey follows a petition
OL,14,Flaunched by a Scottish butcher ahead
OL,15,Fof the World Cup to "make haggis legal
OL,16,Fagain" in the US.
OL,18,FThe petition has gained more than 550
OL,19,Fsignatures since its launch in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
